            "description": "## üìÑ List Applications\n\n**Purpose**: Retrieve a paginated list of job applications with comprehensive filtering and sorting options.\n\n**Features**:\n- ‚úÖ Pagination with configurable page size\n- üîç Multiple filter options\n- üî§ Full-text search across fields\n- üìä Sorting by any field\n- üïê Calculated fields (days since applied)\n\n**Common Use Cases**:\n- View all applications with basic pagination\n- Find applications by company: `?company_name=Google`\n- Search for specific roles: `?search=python engineer`\n- Filter by status: `?status=applied&status=reviewing`\n- Get recent applications: `?sort_by=created_at&sort_order=desc`\n\n**Example Responses**:\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": [...],\n  \"total\": 150,\n  \"page\": 1,\n  \"limit\": 20,\n  \"pages\": 8,\n  \"has_next\": true,\n  \"has_previous\": false\n}\n```"
